readable.content: Brown dog and two black dogs have three-way tug on red object , outdoors . Three dogs are all tugging on the same toy as they stand behind a house . Three large dogs , one brown and the others black , tussle over a red toy in the grass outside a building . two black dogs and a brown dog are tugging at a red object with their mouths . Two black dogs are tugging on a red toy that is in a brown dog 's mouth .
